---
title: Vegetable Jumble with Shrimp and Feta-Topped Arugula Salad
description: Juicy shrimp is the star of this show! Sautéed in garlic butter and seasoned with smoked paprika, they're served up with colourful roasted veg and a peppery arugula side salad.

